data.description: Great Opportunity in Old Mandeville MINUTES from the Causeway Bridge! This 3 Bedroom, 3 Full Bathroom Home is on a Corner Lot in an AMAZING Neighborhood surrounded by the Tammany Trace (a 31-mile remodeled railroad trestle converted into a tree-lined biking/walking/running trail complete with streams and pedestrian bridges), great schools, local restaurants (offering everything from po-boys to prime rib), and shopping! Enjoy the Mandeville lakefront too! Featuring 2000 Living Square Feet and a Large Backyard, this Home is a GEM for anyone looking for prime Northshore living! This Home has NEVER flooded and is in an X Flood Zone. BRAND NEW ROOF! BRAND NEW ENERGY SAVING DOUBLE-PANED WINDOWS (28 total) throughout the Home! CENTRAL A/C SYSTEM updated in 2020 with Lennox 2-stage blower and condenser AND new ducts! Seller Offering $10,000 toward Buyer's Closing Costs and Insurances! The interior needs some love, allowing the new owner(s) to update it to their liking! Under transferrable termite contract with J&J Exterminating. SCHEDULE AN APPOINTMENT TODAY!
